snippet.title: Immortal: Unchained - Chronicles Trailer
snippet.description:
Death is not the end. Immortal: Unchained launches September 7, 2018 on PS4, Xbox One and PC. Pre-order now to receive exclusive in-game content.

Discover more about the lore of Immortal: Unchained in the Chronicles Trailer, featuring an early look at one of the game's cutscenes.
